175,-0.06368962,-0.02938408,0.01246025,-0.00997005,0.00783458,0.00505672,0.06483605,-0.04668912,-0.02024659,0.00907167,0.03494002,0.02034496,0.02037286,0.01143511,-0.02277778,0.01724808,0.02152557,-0.04249429,0.01563727,-0.00129929,0.00981759,0.01948564,-0.07687604,0.05396002,0.01479300,0.00924913,-0.00439691,-0.00924688,-0.03139048,-0.04829146,-0.00449090,-0.02381563,0.04518586,0.03435618,-0.02153130,0.00522208,-0.00186370,0.00951100,-0.07765986,0.03858477,-0.00172076,-0.06707240]',E'Common Issues\n\n1. **ModuleNotFoundError: No module named ''tiktoken''**\n\n   - Install tiktoken explicitly: `uv pip install ''crewai[embeddings]''`\n   - If using embedchain or other tools: `uv pip install ''crewai[tools]''`\n\n2. **Failed building wheel for tiktoken**\n\n   - Ensure Rust compiler is installed (see installation steps above)\n   - For Windows: Verify Visual C++ Build Tools are installed\n   - Try upgrading pip: `uv pip install --upgrade pip`\n   - If issues persist, use a pre-built wheel: `uv pip install tiktoken --prefer-binary`','{"source": "crewai", "version": "0.80", "language": "python", "title": "CrewAI AMP Suite", "section_title": "README", "url": "https://github.com/crewAIInc/crewAI/blob/main/README.md", "topics": "crewai,agents,multi-agent,README", "categories": "ai,agents,orchestration"}');
